'''馬可·艾里亞斯·岡薩雷斯'''（{{lang-en|Marco Elias Gonzales}}，{{bd|1992年|2月16日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於西雅圖水手。他先前曾效力過聖路易紅雀，他在2014年登上大聯盟，2016年因為動了湯米·約翰手術而整季報銷。
==職業生涯==
[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，岡薩雷斯在第一輪19順位被紅雀隊選走。他以185萬美元成功加盟紅雀。
===聖路易紅雀===
====2014年====
6月25日，因為Jaime Garcia受傷，因此球隊將人仍在2A的岡薩雷斯拉上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |last=Ulm |first=Cody |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140623&content_id=81248614&notebook_id=81251000&vkey=notebook_stl&c_id=stl |title=Gonzales' debut doubles as homecoming |publisher=MLB.com |date=June 23, 2014 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714143712/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140623&content_id=81248614&notebook_id=81251000&vkey=notebook_stl&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/events/all_star/y2014/futures_roster.jsp |title=2014 All-Star Futures Game roster |publisher=MLB.com |access-date=July 13, 2014 |archive-date=2016-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115083251/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/events/all_star/y2014/futures_roster.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在生涯首打席就敲出二壘安打，投球方面主投5局失5分無關勝敗。<ref>{{cite web |last=Ulm |first=Cody |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_25_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=stl |title=Cards cap big comeback with clutch two-baggers |publisher=MLB.com |date=June 25, 2014 |access-date=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025518/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_25_slnmlb_colmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>他也成為球隊繼1998年後，第一位從2A跳級直升大聯盟的投手。<ref>{{cite news |title=LHP Marco Gonzalez to debut with Cardinals |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11134514 |access-date=June 26, 2014 |agency=Associated Press |publisher=ESPN.com |date=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714231209/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11134514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月30日，岡薩雷斯拿下大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite web |last=Langosch |first=Jenifer |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_08_31_chnmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=stl#gid=2014_08_30_chnmlb_slnmlb_2&mode=recap&c_id=stl |title=Holliday's swings, big eighth give Cards the split |publisher=MLB.com |date=August 31, 2014 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411165459/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_08_31_chnmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=stl#gid=2014_08_30_chnmlb_slnmlb_2&mode=recap&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他拿下4勝2敗，防禦率4.15。<ref name=majlgstats>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gonzama02.shtml |title=Marco Gonzales statistics and history |website=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=December 20, 2014 |archive-date=2017-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722121339/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/g/gonzama02.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>紅雀在這年順利打進季後賽，岡薩雷斯也成功入選季後賽出賽名單內。他在分區賽以後援身分出賽2場，並都成功拿下勝投。<ref>{{cite web |last=Langosch |first=Jenifer |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_10_07_lanmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=stl#gid=2014_10_07_lanmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=stl |title=Up and Adams: Cards mold NLCS berth out of Clayton |publisher=MLB.com |date=October 7, 2014 |access-date=October 7, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232403/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_10_07_lanmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=stl#gid=2014_10_07_lanmlb_slnmlb_1&mode=recap&c_id=stl |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來他在國聯冠軍賽也有登板，不過投了3局失3分，最終紅雀遭到巨人淘汰。<ref name=majlgstats/>12月份，岡薩雷斯獲選為小聯盟年度最佳投手獎。<ref name=minlgpoy>{{cite web |last=Goold |first=Derrick |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/someone-old-someone-new-are-cards-best/article_05cfb0ce-fd8c-5ae3-bc26-c515193d37b8.html |title=Someone old, someone new are Cards' best |work=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]] |date=December 19, 2014 |access-date=December 20, 2014 |archive-date=2016-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816065155/http://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/someone-old-someone-new-are-cards-best/article_05cfb0ce-fd8c-5ae3-bc26-c515193d37b8.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2015年====
這年岡薩雷斯主要受肩傷所苦，他在小聯盟僅拿下1勝4敗，防禦率5.20。他在9月份擴編再次登上大聯盟，<ref>{{cite news |last=Timmerman |first=Tom |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cardinals-call-up-gonzales-harris-stanley/article_7d2261a9-9dc8-5f9d-9c78-80513d66f522.html |title=Cards win another stunner, beat Nationals 8–5 |newspaper=St. Louis Post-Dispatch |date=September 1, 2015 |access-date=September 4, 2015}}</ref>不過他在球季初次先發投不到3局就掉了4分。<ref>{{cite news |last=Lytle |first=Kevin |url=http://www.coloradoan.com/story/sports/mlb/2015/09/01/marco-gonzales-start/71552432/ |title=Marco Gonzales struggles in MLB season debut |newspaper=Fort Collins Coloradoan |date=September 2, 2015 |access-date=September 2, 2015}}</ref>儘管如此，《棒球美國》仍將他評為紅雀隊上第五出色的新秀。<ref>{{cite web |last=Manuel |first=John |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/st-louis-cardinals-top-10-prospects/ |title=St. Louis Cardinals top 10 prospects |work=[[Baseball_America|Baseball America]] |date=November 16, 2015 |access-date=January 1, 2016 |archive-date=2018-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107055650/https://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/st-louis-cardinals-top-10-prospects/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2016年====
4月13日，岡薩雷斯因為左手肘尺骨附屬韌帶撕裂傷，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2016/04/marco-gonzales-tommy-john-surgery-cardinals.html|title=Cardinals' Marco Gonzales To Undergo Tommy John Surgery|website=MLB Trade Rumors|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095433/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2016/04/marco-gonzales-tommy-john-surgery-cardinals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此進行[[尺骨附屬韌帶重建術|尺骨附屬韌帶重建術]]導致球季報銷。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.denverpost.com/preps/2016/04/20/marco-gonzales-former-5a-lobo-recovering-tommy-john-surgery/19778/|title=Marco Gonzales, former 5A Lobo, recovering from Tommy John surgery|website=Prepped|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025222733/http://blogs.denverpost.com/preps/2016/04/20/marco-gonzales-former-5a-lobo-recovering-tommy-john-surgery/19778/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2017年====
他在6月13日被叫上大聯盟，並在面對釀酒人的雙重賽中登板。這也是他睽違快兩年的初次先發。
===西雅圖水手===
====2017年====
7月21日，紅雀隊將他交易至水手隊，換來[[泰勒·歐尼爾|泰勒·歐尼爾]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenewstribune.com/sports/mlb/seattle-mariners/article162898233.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2018-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913112251/https://www.thenewstribune.com/sports/mlb/seattle-mariners/article162898233.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在8月6日完成在水手隊的初次登板，他先發面對皇家隊主投4局失5分，送出5次三振。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/KCA/KCA201708061.shtml|title=Seattle Mariners at Kansas City Royals Box Score, August 6, 2017|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819085854/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/KCA/KCA201708061.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他在水手隊先發7場比賽，拿下1勝1敗，防禦率5.40。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=gonzama02&t=p&year=2017|title=Marco Gonzales 2017 Pitching Game Logs|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112234413/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=gonzama02&t=p&year=2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====2018年====
在春訓投出1勝1敗，防禦率2.08的成績後，岡薩雷斯入選水手隊的4號先發。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lytle |first=Kevin |url=https://www.coloradoan.com/story/sports/high-school/baseball/2018/03/29/rocky-mountain-grad-makes-seattle-mariners-starting-rotation/469816002/ |title=Rocky Mountain grad Marco Gonzales makes Seattle Mariners' starting rotation |publisher=Coloradoan.com |date=March 29, 2018}}</ref>6月29日，他面對皇家隊投滿9局僅失1分拿下生涯首次完投勝。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SEA/SEA201806290.shtml|title=Kansas City Royals at Seattle Mariners Box Score, June 29, 2018|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218105746/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SEA/SEA201806290.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在上半季投出10勝5敗，防禦率3.41，不過他到了下半季表現有些走樣，只拿下3勝4敗，防禦率5.23。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/split.fcgi?id=gonzama02&t=p&year=2018|title=Marco Gonzales 2018 Pitching Splits|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122052447/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/split.fcgi?id=gonzama02&t=p&year=2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2019年====
這年水手隊的開幕戰於東京巨蛋舉行，岡薩雷斯再度擔綱開幕戰先發。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/mariners/news/marco-gonzales-to-start-mariners-opening-day|title=Gonzales to start Mariners' opener; Kikuchi in G2|website=MLB.com}}</ref>這也是水手隊近10年來由「國王」[[費利克斯·赫南德茲|費利克斯·赫南德茲]]以外的投手擔任開幕戰先發，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/felix-hernandezs-historic-decadelong-streak-will-end-on-opening-day-035430102.html|title=Felix Hernandez's remarkable opening day streak is coming to an end|website=sports.yahoo.com|language=en-CA|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808202251/https://sports.yahoo.com/felix-hernandezs-historic-decadelong-streak-will-end-on-opening-day-035430102.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而岡薩雷斯也以6局失4分奪勝。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK201903200.shtml|title=Seattle Mariners at Oakland Athletics Box Score, March 20, 2019|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-10|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228065823/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK201903200.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也是這年水手隊唯一一位表現算穩定的投手，他拿下16勝13敗，防禦率3.99。
====2020年====
這年岡薩雷斯再次擔任開幕戰先發，他面對太空人主投4.1局失3分，最終球隊獲勝。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariners-Astros box score July 24th, 2020|url=https://www.mlb.com/gameday/mariners-vs-astros/2020/07/24/631438#game_state=final,lock_state=final,game_tab=box,game=631438|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108163813/https://www.mlb.com/gameday/mariners-vs-astros/2020/07/24/631438#game_state=final,lock_state=final,game_tab=box,game=631438|dead-url=no}}</ref>而這場先發也是他整季投最短局數的一場先發，其中他在8月31日更是再次投出完投勝。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariners - Angels box score August 31st, 2020|url=https://www.mlb.com/gameday/mariners-vs-angels/2020/08/31/631374#game_state=final,lock_state=final,game_tab=box,game=631374|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302212410/https://www.mlb.com/gameday/mariners-vs-angels/2020/08/31/631374#game_state=final,lock_state=final,game_tab=box,game=631374|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他拿下7勝2敗，防禦率3.10。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2020-pitching-leaders.shtml|title=2020 American League Pitching Leaders|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310164403/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/2020-pitching-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==個人生活==
岡薩雷斯的父親法蘭克曾於1989年大聯盟選秀會上被老虎隊選中，後來他在小聯盟打了10年球，目前在洛磯隊的1A球隊擔任投手教練。<ref name=denverpost>{{cite web |last=Frei |first=Terry |url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_23357824/former-rocky-mountain-h-s-star-marco-gonzales |title=Marco Gonzales likely first-round pick in 2013 MLB draft after starring for Rocky Mountain H.S., Gonzaga |work=[[The_Denver_Post|The Denver Post]] |date=June 2, 2013 |access-date=June 2, 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310023133/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_23357824/former-rocky-mountain-h-s-star-marco-gonzales |dead-url=no }}</ref>而岡薩雷斯的哥哥艾力克斯高中時也曾打過棒球隊。<ref name=Branch>{{cite news |last1=Branch |first1=John |title=A mother's phone buzzes: Her son is in again |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/17/sports/baseball/cardinals-pitcher-marco-gonzales-gives-family-an-october-surprise.html?rref=sports&module=Ribbon&version=origin&region=Header&action=click&contentCollection=Sports&pgtype=article |access-date=October 16, 2014 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] Company |date=October 16, 2014 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329074618/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/17/sports/baseball/cardinals-pitcher-marco-gonzales-gives-family-an-october-surprise.html?rref=sports&module=Ribbon&version=origin&region=Header&action=click&contentCollection=Sports&pgtype=article |dead-url=no }}</ref>

岡薩雷斯從小就是洛磯隊的球迷，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/midwest/story/cardinals-gonzales-set-to-debut-in-familiar-park-062414-2|title=Cardinals' Gonzales set to debut in familiar park|first1=foxsports|last1=Jun 24|first2=2014 at 10:10p|last2=ET|date=June 24, 2014|website=FOX Sports|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2020-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011015435/https://www.foxsports.com/midwest/story/cardinals-gonzales-set-to-debut-in-familiar-park-062414-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>他於2015年結婚，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.king5.com/article/news/local/marco-and-monica-gonzales-launch-peanut-butter-drive/281-20eeb9d7-f0da-412b-bf79-727b96475293 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920150703/https://www.king5.com/article/news/local/marco-and-monica-gonzales-launch-peanut-butter-drive/281-20eeb9d7-f0da-412b-bf79-727b96475293 |dead-url=no }}</ref>目前定居在西雅圖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://theathletic.com/771676/2019/01/17/marco-gonzales-is-at-home-in-seattle-and-comfortable-as-foundation-of-mariners-rebuild/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108005303/https://theathletic.com/771676/2019/01/17/marco-gonzales-is-at-home-in-seattle-and-comfortable-as-foundation-of-mariners-rebuild/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
